                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The Sihedron drone is reduced to 0 Hit Points</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The drone emits a metallic screech followed by a steady ticking sound. On its next turn, the Sihedron drone flies up to 30 feet toward the nearest foe and explodes, dealing @Damage[3d6[piercing]] damage in a 5-foot radius (@Check[reflex|dc:18|basic] save). Its integrated aeon stone is destroyed, along with any information the drone recorded. An adjacent creature can stop the self-destruct sequence by succeeding at a @Check[crafting|dc:18] or @Check[thievery|dc:18] check to Disable a Device.</p>"
                },
